    <div class="container black-trans-bg">
      <h1 class="mainTitle">BomberBlock</h1>
      <p>
           BomberBlock is a real-time multiplayer rpg combat game. <b>The main goal</b> : Eleminate the most enemies and get the best score 
           you can to be listed on the Ultimate BomberKillers. 
           The name <b>BomberBlock</b> came at first because it was only suppose to be a cubic world with cubic bombs. The name 
           stayed, even though many things have changed since the beginning.
      </p>
      <p>
          BomberBlock was developed for the most recent web technologies, as NodeJS and Chrome's V8.
      </p>
<h3 class="smallTitle">The game</h3>
      <p>Spawn in a small world and compete against other players for a place on podium. Eleminate the most enemy and conquert the base the longger you can to score bigger points!</p>
      <p>By killing other players, you score points, but you also make them drop some money. You better collect it fast before
        anyone do it first!
      </p>
      <p>Money can be exchanged for ammunition int the Market of the setting menu (up-right corner).</p>
      <p>A new cryptocurrency have been added to the game to help on playabilty. Its called Sweatcoin, and its based on the real cryto with the same name.
        Sweatcoins may be mined while sweating only. To gain some, you will need to walk or run! Sweatcoin are also easy to collect, and at any moment, you can exchange it against money.
        Obviously, the exchange rate is low, since today's sweatcoin's value is realy low!
      </p>
      <p>In need of life or other equipment, as bullets or shield, you can refer to one of the 4 Perk Stations in the map. The perks (Instant improvement) are spawn randomly, at random moment.
        Be sure to stick arround one if you are in need!
      </p>
