      <h2 class="subtitle">How To Play</h1>
      <p>
        BomberBlock is super easy to play! Just go to <b><i>Game</i></b> page, login with your name and your color, and Find a Game!
      </p>
      <p>
        Once you are in a game, Survive, defend your self and try to stay long enought on the <b><i>Base</i></b> to gain
        many points!
      </p>
      <p>Movements are a bit tricky. Basically, the player's always following the pointer (mouse). When you press <b><i>W</i></b>,
      you are walking forward in pointer's direction. Do not forget about it!
      </p>
      <p>To Jump, press <b><i>Spacebar</i></b>. You can double-jump, but it's a bit tricky!</p>
      <p>
        To <b><i>Shoot</i></b>, left-click your mice!
      </p>
      <p>To see the score board, hold <b><i>TAB</i></b></p>
      <p>
        To see setting panel, press <b><i>P</i></b>  or click on the gear on the top-right corner. In the settings, 
      there is the market section where you can buy bullets or exchange all of your sweatcoins. The other section is to control
      music : you can mute or change de volume, get previous or next song.
      </p>
      <p>
        If you wish to <b><i>Chat</i></b> with others players, press <b><i>C</i></b> to show the chat panel. Quick keyboard 
        shortcut have been made to accelerate playability. When Chat is visible, press <b><i>Enter</i></b> to focus on the chat input, 
        press again to send your new message, and press again to remove focus from the chat. These step must be done to prevent 
        using important keys of the game, as the movement (WASD).
      </p>
